 <br />
I agree about the ER thing, but hey, sometimes when youre hurting bad enough, you will try anything.  Bad WDs will make you lose every ounce of shame you even dreamed about having <img src="images/smile/smiley2.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Smiley2" class="inlineimg" />
